currency_code.docs: The currency code for the workspace (e.g., USD, GBP, EUR)

workspaces.yml.rawContents:
imports:
  root: __package__.yml
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    createAWorkspace:
      path: /workspaces
      method: POST
      docs: Creates a new workspace and adds the user as a Workspace Admin.
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Create a workspace
      request:
        name: CreateWorkspace
        body:
          properties:
            title:
              type: string
              docs: The title of the workspace
            currency_code:
              type: optional<string>
              docs: The currency code for the workspace (e.g., USD, GBP, EUR)
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Workspace created successfully
        type: root.Workspace
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - name: simple_workspace
          headers:
            Authorization: Authorization
          request:
            title: My new workspace
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              title: title
              currency_code: currency_code
        - name: great_british_pounds_workspace
          headers:
            Authorization: Authorization
          request:
            title: My workspace using British Pounds
            currency_code: GBP
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              title: title
              currency_code: currency_code
        - name: united_states_dollars_workspace
          headers:
            Authorization: Authorization
          request:
            title: My workspace using US Dollars
            currency_code: USD
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              title: title
              currency_code: currency_code
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml
